				<pubDate>Sun, 12 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>https://example.org/posts/images-and-lightbox/</guid>
				<description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;external-image&#34;&gt;&#xA;  External image&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Click the image to open in a lightbox.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500530855697-b586d89ba3ee?auto=format&amp;amp;fit=crop&amp;amp;w=1400&amp;amp;q=60&#34; class=&#34;lightbox-image&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img src=&#34;https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500530855697-b586d89ba3ee?auto=format&amp;amp;fit=crop&amp;amp;w=1400&amp;amp;q=60&#34; alt=&#34;Mountain lake&#34; title=&#34;Open full size&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;figcaption&gt;Open full size&lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;local-image-note&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Local image note&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;For page bundles, put images beside &lt;code&gt;index.md&lt;/code&gt; and reference by filename only to get dimensions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
